{
  "stem": "12447.3",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So here, we were four people trying to get out of the ghetto-- my mother and father, my sister, and myself.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My sister was chosen the first one to go.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she-- at that time, I found out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because until that time, I didn't know that my uncle that was the painter became a superintendent of this project, of this building over there.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he was taking care of the building.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And on the roof, they had contraband going through the roof.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So until that point, I didn't know what he was doing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't see each other.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I didn't know that it was possible through his roof to get out on the Polish side.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they decided that my sister will go one evening to my uncle, and she'll make her way through the roof, and go to the town where my father comes from, to Siedlce, which was 100 kilometers, took about three hours by train to get there.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But she had no problem getting any place.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She spoke good Polish.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So she made her way to my uncle.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And a few weeks later, we got a-- we got words that she made it to the town of Siedlce.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she got over there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She was safe and everything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The next one, I had to go.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Now, I was too small to travel alone at that time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So they decided that my aunt, the barber's wife, would travel with me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Now, she was also a very fair complexion, kind of blondish looking, spoke very well Polish.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So there was no danger for her to go with me or for me to go with her.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "She was a perfect situation for both of us to go out.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We went out.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "In the evening, we came to my uncle.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
